{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, this property is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two foci","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically, this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property has no effect if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value other than "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view with an animated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"transition. If you don’t want to animate the change, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method instead.","type":"text"}]}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L752"},"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"targetCoordinate","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)targetCoordinate","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"title":"MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source